== 評價 ==
《初戀潛水艇》得到了評論家正面的評價。《[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]》根據154條評論，獲得了88%的新鮮度，平均得分7.4 / 10。該網站的評論家一致認為電影：「將青少年的狀態描寫的時髦、風趣，[[理察·艾歐阿德|理察·艾歐阿德]]有值得關注的天賦。」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/submarine-2010/ |title=Submarine |work=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher={{tsl|en|Flixster||Flixster}} |access-date=2020-05-20 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116064200/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/submarine-2010 }}</ref> 在《[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]》上，將100分依加權平均分給主流影評的評論，根據37個評論，電影獲得平均得分為76 / 100，顯示為「普遍好評」。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/submarine |title=Submarine |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |access-date=2014-06-17 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023634/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/submarine }}</ref> 影評[[羅傑·伊伯特|羅傑·伊伯特]]給予3 / 4顆星，並評論：「《初戀潛水艇》並不是一部平淡無奇的青少年色情喜劇。」<ref>{{cite news |last=Haws |first=Marie |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20110608/REVIEWS/110609987 |title=Submarine Movie Review & Film Summary (2011) | Roger Ebert |publisher=Rogerebert.suntimes.com |date=2011-06-08 |access-date=2013-11-28 |archive-date=2013-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130312012935/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20110608%2FREVIEWS%2F110609987 }}</ref>

